You mess with one Buffalo,

01:44.125 --> 01:46.041
you mess

01:44.125 --> 01:46.041
with the whole herd.

01:46.083 --> 01:47.250
- Yeah.

01:47.291 --> 01:49.458
- We just have to

01:47.291 --> 01:49.458
figure out how.

