- Hey, guys, just reminding you,

01:50.792 --> 01:52.417
it's Mom's birthday tomorrow,

01:52.458 --> 01:54.750
and every year we--we mess up

01:52.458 --> 01:54.750
by not getting her a gift,

01:54.792 --> 01:56.083
but not this year.

01:54.792 --> 01:56.083
Don't forget.

01:56.125 --> 01:57.083
Get her something nice.

01:57.125 --> 01:59.875
I, uh...

01:59.917 --> 02:03.333
I got her this fancy

01:59.917 --> 02:03.333
