Huh?

02:03.375 --> 02:04.583
Ooh.

02:04.625 --> 02:06.250
Ah.

02:06.291 --> 02:08.208
Ooh, ah.

02:08.250 --> 02:10.291
She's gonna love it.

02:08.250 --> 02:10.291
So you guys on board?

02:10.333 --> 02:11.417
- Yeah.

02:10.333 --> 02:11.417
- Yeah, sure am.

02:11.458 --> 02:12.875
- Of course, got ya.

02:11.458 --> 02:12.875
- Okay, good.

02:12.917 --> 02:13.625
[box snaps shut]

02:12.917 --> 02:13.625
Ooh!

02:13.667 --> 02:16.250
Ah.

02:16.291 --> 02:17.542
- I got it!

02:17.583 --> 02:19.250
They messed with our mascot,

02:19.291 --> 02:21.208
so we'll mess with theirs.

02:21.250 --> 02:23.542
Let's steal their war pig.

