- This is so exciting!

03:02.542 --> 03:05.000
I can't believe

03:02.542 --> 03:05.000
we pulled off this pignapping.

03:05.041 --> 03:06.583
- This is just phase one.

03:06.625 --> 03:07.792
- Phase two is to get him

03:07.834 --> 03:09.500
in an Edgewood

03:07.834 --> 03:09.500
cheerleader costume

03:09.542 --> 03:11.500
