[cell phone chimes]

03:16.375 --> 03:18.792
Dooley's on his way over

03:16.375 --> 03:18.792
with a wig and tiny dress now.

03:18.834 --> 03:20.750
- I feel so alive!

03:20.792 --> 03:22.583
Revenge has changed me.

03:22.625 --> 03:25.458
[deeper voice]

03:22.625 --> 03:25.458
I'm Bad Boy Ricky now,

03:25.500 --> 03:28.166
and I'm not afraid of anything.

03:25.500 --> 03:28.166
[car door slams outside]

03:28.208 --> 03:29.542
[shouting]

03:28.208 --> 03:29.542
Ah! It's Nelly and the War Pigs!

03:29.583 --> 03:30.625
Everybody hide!

03:30.667 --> 03:32.417
Move!

03:32.458 --> 03:34.583
- Oh, no.

03:32.458 --> 03:34.583
Maybe they saw us take the pig

03:34.625 --> 03:35.834
and followed us home.

03:35.875 --> 03:37.458
- Nobody followed us.

03:37.500 --> 03:38.709
[doorknob rattles]

03:38.750 --> 03:40.750
- They followed us!

03:40.792 --> 03:42.834
- Come on, run!

03:42.875 --> 03:43.875
[all breathing heavily]

03:43.917 --> 03:47.083
- That was close.

03:47.125 --> 03:48.750
- Wait.

03:47.125 --> 03:48.750
Where's the pig?

03:48.792 --> 03:50.041
- [groans]

03:50.083 --> 03:52.750
[pig snorting and squealing]

03:52.792 --> 03:55.125
- Anne? Kids?

03:52.792 --> 03:55.125
Anybody home?

03:55.166 --> 03:57.083
- That's not Nelly.

03:55.166 --> 03:57.083
That's Dad.

03:57.125 --> 03:58.500
- Should we tell him

03:57.125 --> 03:58.500
about the pig?

03:58.542 --> 04:00.417
- What?

03:58.542 --> 04:00.417
No one's telling Dad anything.

04:00.458 --> 04:02.125
- So we're just going to

04:00.458 --> 04:02.125
lie to him?

04:02.166 --> 04:03.667
- Isn't the chance

04:02.166 --> 04:03.667
of getting payback on Nelly

04:03.709 --> 04:07.166
and the War Pigs

04:03.709 --> 04:07.166
worth telling one little lie?

04:07.208 --> 04:08.917
- Bad Boy Ricky would do it.

04:08.959 --> 04:11.083
- Yeah, he would...

04:11.125 --> 04:13.625
[deeper voice]

04:11.125 --> 04:13.625
And he'd like it.

04:13.667 --> 04:15.417
I'm in.

04:15.458 --> 04:17.417
Let the lying begin.

04:17.458 --> 04:18.917
- Okay, easy, Bad Boy.

04:18.959 --> 04:20.792
We're only telling

04:18.959 --> 04:20.792
one little lie.

04:20.834 --> 04:22.083
Oh, here.

04:20.834 --> 04:22.083
[pig snorting]

04:22.125 --> 04:23.750
We can hide the pig in here.

04:23.792 --> 04:24.667
Dad will never know.

04:24.709 --> 04:25.917
- Good idea.

04:25.959 --> 04:27.542
Things get lost in here.

04:27.583 --> 04:30.750
I left a burrito

04:27.583 --> 04:30.750
in a jacket over a month ago.

04:30.792 --> 04:33.041
Still haven't found it.

04:33.083 --> 04:34.834
- [sniffs]

04:33.083 --> 04:34.834
Ugh.

04:34.875 --> 04:36.834
Found it.

04:39.125 --> 04:40.709
- Hey, what are you doing

04:39.125 --> 04:40.709
in the closet?

04:40.750 --> 04:42.917
- Uh...just hanging out.

04:42.959 --> 04:44.500
<i>[bell dings]</i>

04:44.542 --> 04:46.542
- Yeah.

04:46.583 --> 04:49.959
We realized we have a whole room

04:46.583 --> 04:49.959
that we never spend any time in.

04:50.000 --> 04:51.250
<i>[bell dings]</i>

04:51.291 --> 04:52.875
[whispering]

04:51.291 --> 04:52.875
Okay. Two little lies.

04:52.917 --> 04:54.792
- Well, stay out of there.

04:52.917 --> 04:54.792
I got important stuff

04:54.834 --> 04:56.333
in that closet.

04:54.834 --> 04:56.333
Now come on.

04:56.375 --> 04:58.208
Help me set up this cake

04:56.375 --> 04:58.208
for your mom's birthday.

04:58.250 --> 05:01.792
- Ooh, Mom's birthday.

04:58.250 --> 05:01.792
When is it?

05:01.834 --> 05:03.166
- Today.

05:03.208 --> 05:04.375
- It is?

05:04.417 --> 05:06.208
- What--were you even

05:04.417 --> 05:06.208
listening to me

05:06.250 --> 05:08.166
when I told you yesterday?

05:08.208 --> 05:10.083
Hey, kids.

05:08.208 --> 05:10.083
Just reminding ya.

05:10.125 --> 05:11.250
Blah, blah, blah.

05:10.125 --> 05:11.250
Dad stuff.

05:11.291 --> 05:13.917
Dad stuff, shiny thing.

05:11.291 --> 05:13.917
Blah...

05:13.959 --> 05:16.417
- Of course we were

05:13.959 --> 05:16.417
listening to you.

05:16.458 --> 05:17.500
<i>[bell dings]</i>

05:17.542 --> 05:18.875
- Good, 'cause your mother

05:17.542 --> 05:18.875
deserves

05:18.917 --> 05:20.750
a great birthday present.

05:20.792 --> 05:22.709
- Which we definitely got her.

05:22.750 --> 05:23.625
<i>[bell dings]</i>

05:23.667 --> 05:24.917
- [gasps]

05:24.959 --> 05:27.875
all: Happy Birthday!

05:27.917 --> 05:28.834
- Aw, you remembered.

05:28.875 --> 05:30.917
- Of course we did.

05:30.959 --> 05:32.458
- We also remembered

05:32.500 --> 05:35.125
your favorite

05:32.500 --> 05:35.125
birthday tradition:

05:35.166 --> 05:37.250
cake for breakfast.

05:37.291 --> 05:38.917
- Oh, Tom.

05:37.291 --> 05:38.917
You shouldn't have.

05:38.959 --> 05:40.542
- Well.

05:38.959 --> 05:40.542
- [laughing]

05:40.583 --> 05:42.083
Hmm.

05:42.125 --> 05:44.834
"Happy Birthday for Tom?"

05:44.875 --> 05:46.208
- What?

05:44.875 --> 05:46.208
What?

05:46.250 --> 05:47.709
No!

05:47.750 --> 05:49.709
I said it was supposed to say

05:47.750 --> 05:49.709
"Happy Birthday,"

05:49.750 --> 05:51.041
and the order was for Tom.

05:51.083 --> 05:53.792
Not "for Tom."

05:51.083 --> 05:53.792
For Tom!

05:53.834 --> 05:56.583
- It's okay.

05:53.834 --> 05:56.583
It's still cake for breakfast.

05:56.625 --> 05:57.959
- No, no, no, no!

05:56.625 --> 05:57.959
Wait, wait, wait, wait.

05:58.000 --> 05:59.208
No, no, no, no, no, no.

05:59.250 --> 06:02.208
You deserve better.

06:02.250 --> 06:04.500
Oh.

06:02.250 --> 06:04.500
- No.

06:04.542 --> 06:08.083
- Which is why we all got you

06:04.542 --> 06:08.083
amazing gifts.

06:08.125 --> 06:09.250
I'm gonna get mine...

06:09.291 --> 06:10.667
mmm, out of the closet.

06:10.709 --> 06:11.834
[kids exclaiming]

06:11.875 --> 06:14.709
- Tom, I really wanted

06:11.875 --> 06:14.709
that cake.

06:14.750 --> 06:16.834
- [exclaims]

06:14.750 --> 06:16.834
Pig! Pig in the house!

06:16.875 --> 06:18.500
- Tom!

06:18.542 --> 06:20.792
- No, no.

06:18.542 --> 06:20.792
Real pig in the house!

06:20.834 --> 06:22.041
- [exclaims]

06:22.083 --> 06:25.333
[pig snorting and squealing]

06:25.375 --> 06:26.834
Who brought this pig

06:25.375 --> 06:26.834
into my house?

06:26.875 --> 06:29.625
- Well, it definitely

06:26.875 --> 06:29.625
wasn't me.

06:29.667 --> 06:32.875
- Because I love pigs!

06:34.750 --> 06:37.709
- Well, that's why

06:34.750 --> 06:37.709
we got one for you.

06:37.750 --> 06:38.875
<i>[bell dings]</i>

06:38.917 --> 06:41.917
- kids: Happy birthday, Mom!

06:41.959 --> 06:44.041
<i>♪</i>

06:46.709 --> 06:48.834
<i>[upbeat music]</i>

06:48.875 --> 06:50.583
- Guys,

06:48.875 --> 06:50.583
what a thoughtful present.

06:50.625 --> 06:52.417
Did you get me a pig

06:50.625 --> 06:52.417
because you knew I had one

06:52.458 --> 06:54.750
as a little girl growing up

06:52.458 --> 06:54.750
on the farm?

06:54.792 --> 06:56.667
- Uh...yeah.

06:56.709 --> 06:57.709
<i>[bell dings]</i>

06:57.750 --> 06:59.041
Right, guys?

06:59.083 --> 07:00.166
- Uh, yes.

06:59.083 --> 07:00.166
That is true.

07:00.208 --> 07:02.083
- Totally.

07:00.208 --> 07:02.083
- Mae helped too.

07:02.125 --> 07:03.417
- Why'd you bring me into it?

07:03.458 --> 07:05.083
- Sorry, if Bad Boy Ricky

07:03.458 --> 07:05.083
goes down,

07:05.125 --> 07:07.375
he's taking everybody with him.

07:07.417 --> 07:09.667
- Well...

07:07.417 --> 07:09.667
[sighs]

07:09.709 --> 07:12.291
I got you a thoughtful gift

07:09.709 --> 07:12.291
too, Anne.

07:12.333 --> 07:14.041
But it looks like

07:12.333 --> 07:14.041
our porky friend

07:14.083 --> 07:16.333
made a meal out of it

07:14.083 --> 07:16.333
in the closet.

07:16.375 --> 07:17.333
[snorting]

07:17.375 --> 07:19.750
[knocking at door]

07:19.792 --> 07:22.000
- Hey, guys.

07:19.792 --> 07:22.000
all: Hey, Dooley.

07:22.041 --> 07:24.000
- Happy birthday, Mrs. H.

07:24.041 --> 07:26.375
- Well, thank you, Dooley.

07:26.417 --> 07:29.208
- Yeah.

07:26.417 --> 07:29.208
Thanks, Dooley.

07:29.250 --> 07:31.542
- Now down to business.

07:31.583 --> 07:33.000
You got someplace we can talk?

07:33.041 --> 07:35.000
- Yeah.

07:33.041 --> 07:35.000
Have you seen our closet?

07:35.041 --> 07:36.000
[laughs nervously]

07:36.041 --> 07:37.667
[whispering]

07:36.041 --> 07:37.667
Closet.

07:40.750 --> 07:41.959
- They hang out in there now.

07:42.000 --> 07:45.458
[pig snorting]

07:45.500 --> 07:47.000
- I don't like

07:45.500 --> 07:47.000
to toot my own horn,

07:47.041 --> 07:49.792
but this is a Dooley doozy.

07:49.834 --> 07:52.625
So...toot.

07:52.667 --> 07:56.250
One pig-sized cheerleader outfit

07:52.667 --> 07:56.250
as requested.

07:56.291 --> 07:58.875
Go, Buffaloes!

07:58.917 --> 08:01.375
- Look, Dooley, there's been

07:58.917 --> 08:01.375
