08:01.417 --> 08:03.625
Turns out--

08:01.417 --> 08:03.625
- Bup-bup-bup.

08:03.667 --> 08:05.792
I only need to know

08:03.667 --> 08:05.792
what I need to know.

08:05.834 --> 08:08.625
- [laughs]

08:05.834 --> 08:08.625
Bad Boy Ricky gets it.

08:08.667 --> 08:11.709
This way, you're off the hook

08:08.667 --> 08:11.709
if the law gets wise.

08:11.750 --> 08:13.792
Nice.

08:13.834 --> 08:17.125
- He's calling himself

08:13.834 --> 08:17.125
"Bad Boy Ricky" now?

08:17.166 --> 08:19.583
- Yes, he is.

08:19.625 --> 08:21.709
- Dooley's gonna be honest

08:19.625 --> 08:21.709
with you.

08:21.750 --> 08:24.542
It's a tough sell.

08:24.583 --> 08:25.667
[closet door opens, closes]

08:25.709 --> 08:27.166
- What are we going to do?

08:27.208 --> 08:29.625
- If we still want to be

08:27.208 --> 08:29.625
the school heroes,

08:29.667 --> 08:31.166
we're gonna have to get

08:29.667 --> 08:31.166
that pig away from Mom

08:31.208 --> 08:33.083
so we can finish our revenge.

08:33.125 --> 08:34.333
- But how?

08:34.375 --> 08:35.750
<i>[dog barking]</i>

08:35.792 --> 08:37.542
- Squishy!

08:37.583 --> 08:39.125
We'll convince Mom this house

08:37.583 --> 08:39.125
isn't big enough

08:39.166 --> 08:40.709
for Squishy and the pig.

08:42.625 --> 08:44.875
- Dooley, this is lovely.

08:44.917 --> 08:46.959
How did you find a picture

08:44.917 --> 08:46.959
of my grandmother?

08:47.000 --> 08:49.375
- Bup-bup-bup.

08:49.417 --> 08:52.667
- I got her a necklace first.

08:52.709 --> 08:55.291
- That's a good, good boy.

08:52.709 --> 08:55.291
[dog growling]

08:55.333 --> 08:57.709
- Oh, no, Mom,

08:55.333 --> 08:57.709
it looks like Squishy

08:57.750 --> 08:59.417
doesn't like the pig.

08:59.458 --> 09:03.083
- I hate to say it, but we might

08:59.458 --> 09:03.083
have to give the pig back.

09:03.125 --> 09:05.041
[dog barking]

09:03.125 --> 09:05.041
- Squishy agrees.

09:05.083 --> 09:07.208
- No, back on the farm,

09:05.083 --> 09:07.208
it always took a while

09:07.250 --> 09:09.083
for a pig to warm up to a pup.

09:09.125 --> 09:10.166
They'll love each other

09:09.125 --> 09:10.166
by the time

09:10.208 --> 09:12.000
we take the family portrait.

09:12.041 --> 09:13.333
- Whose family portrait?

09:13.375 --> 09:15.250
- Ours.

09:13.375 --> 09:15.250
Don't you remember?

09:15.291 --> 09:16.291
It's my birthday gift to myself.

09:16.333 --> 09:17.500
We're taking it this afternoon

09:17.542 --> 09:19.083
when Nicky gets back from camp.

09:19.125 --> 09:20.375
I told you about it yesterday.

09:20.417 --> 09:21.792
[kids chanting

09:20.417 --> 09:21.792
"Steal their pig!"]

